12d ago / 12:56 AM UTC

GENEVA ‚Äî The United Nations says it has confirmed at least 240 civilian casualties, including at least 64 people killed, in the fighting in Ukraine that erupted since Russia‚Äôs invasion ‚Äî though it believed the ‚Äúreal figures are considerably higher‚Äù because many reports of casualties remain to be confirmed.

